data.description: Multi generational home! There is an entire living area in the finished basement with 2 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, washer/dryer, refrigerator, sink, cabinets, microwave, stove, and a living room with a fireplace. The finished basement has its own entrance door also! This home is truly a great fit for someone looking for a mother in law quarters living situation. The detached garage also has a work space above with power.
